des: This is just the skill for both the cat lover and cat hater. Listen to a bad cat joke one after another. What could possibly be more purrrrrfect! What better use can anyone think of for the Echo than for it to tell you HORRIBLE cat jokes. Well, wait no longer! The skill has arrived, I am sure that "Cat Jokes" will meet all your bad cat joke needs.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
